    <readme>
      <![CDATA[uSync for Umbraco 6 v1.6.Mayfly Edition
=======================================
uSync is a umbraco DB to/from disk syncing tool. 

uSync will write out:
  - DocumentTypes, 
	- Macros, 
	- DataTypes,
	- Dictionary Items, 
	- Languages, 
	- Templates
	- Stylesheets 
	
When they are on disk they can be added to source control
It also reads the same files from disk and adds them to the umbraco install - so you can move things between installations.
]]>
    </readme>
